	
FOOD SYSTEM	
Food.class falls through the water with a nutrition variable, as it goes down nutrition decreases, as does the speed at which it falls.
Creatures attack eachother based on how much food they need and the amount of food nearby, this nearby food also makes them teritorial, food gives energy to
reproduce and move.

NUTRITION SYSTEM
Use X energy per tick, must replenish, must use alot to reproduce, offspring remembers reproduction energy levels and reproduces at those levels. 
Offspring have same remaining energy as parent, so if parent has child with low energy child will have low energy etc.

WATER COLUMN
Side scrolling with up and down representing the water column.

SET SERVER.CLASS TO NEW SERVER BEFORE PRESSING PLAY;

DEPTH METER USING data/terrain/tiles.png with arrow denoting depth(readout below).

